{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.110\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">大衛的詩。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">耶和華所揀選之王</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.110.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>耶和華對我主說：</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">「你坐在我的右邊，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">等我使你仇敵作你的腳凳。」</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.110.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>耶和華必使你從<span class=\"pn\">錫安</span>伸出你能力的權杖；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">你務要在仇敵中掌權。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.110.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>你在聖山上掌權的日子，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">你的子民必甘心跟隨；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\">從晨曦初現，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">你就有清晨的甘露。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.110.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>耶和華起了誓，絕不改變：</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">「你是照著<span class=\"pn\">麥基洗德</span>的體系永遠為祭司。」</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.110.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>在你右邊的主，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">當他發怒的日子，必打傷列王。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.110.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>他要審判列國，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">屍首就佈滿各處；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">他要痛擊遍地的領袖。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.110.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup>他要喝路旁的河水，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">因此必抬起頭來。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}